#. <section class="sutta" id="sn1.71"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn1.71:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 1"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 1"

#. </p><p>
#. VAR: 8. Chetvāvagga → jhatvāvaggo (bj, pts2) | ghatvāvaggo (s1-3)
msgctxt "sn1.71:0.2"
msgid "8. Chetvāvagga"
msgstr "8. Incinerated"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 71. Chetvāsutta → jhatvāsuttaṃ (bj, pts2) | ghatvāsuttaṃ (s1-3)
msgctxt "sn1.71:0.3"
msgid "71. Chetvāsutta"
msgstr "71. Incinerated"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.93"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn1.71:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn1.71:1.2"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho sā devatā bhagavantaṃ gāthāya ajjhabhāsi:"
msgstr "Standing to one side, that deity addressed the Buddha in verse:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
#. VAR: chetvā → jhatvā (bj, pts2) | ghatvā (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "sn1.71:2.1"
msgid "“Kiṃsu chetvā sukhaṃ seti,"
msgstr "“When what is incinerated do you sleep at ease?"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.71:2.2"
msgid "kiṃsu chetvā na socati;"
msgstr "When what is incinerated is there no sorrow?"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.71:2.3"
msgid "Kissassu ekadhammassa,"
msgstr "What’s the one thing, Gotama,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.71:2.4"
msgid "vadhaṃ rocesi gotamā”ti."
msgstr "whose killing you approve?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn1.71:3.1"
msgid "“Kodhaṃ chetvā sukhaṃ seti,"
msgstr "“When anger’s incinerated you sleep at ease."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.71:3.2"
msgid "kodhaṃ chetvā na socati;"
msgstr "When anger’s incinerated there is no sorrow."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.71:3.3"
msgid "Kodhassa visamūlassa,"
msgstr "O deity, anger has a poisoned root"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.71:3.4"
msgid "madhuraggassa devate;"
msgstr "and a honey tip."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.71:3.5"
msgid "Vadhaṃ ariyā pasaṃsanti,"
msgstr "The noble ones praise its killing,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn1.71:3.6"
msgid "tañhi chetvā na socatī”ti."
msgstr "for when it’s incinerated there is no sorrow.”"
